<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="16Feb1939"><font color="red">16 February 1939</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on): Very many thanks for your letter of February 12th with which you sent me Mr Joyce&apos;s final corrections for the title-page. I am arranging, as he wishes, for his name to be printed on a separate line from the word &ldquo;by&rdquo; and for it to be a size smaller &hellip; actual bulk &hellip; before binding, will be 1 7&frasl;16 inches &hellip; Yes &hellip; Monsieur Gillet an unbound advance copy. </div>
